data.description: DON'T MISS THIS WELL MAINTAINED 4BD, 2BA HOME IN LEHIGH ACRES!  Come enjoy the country and all it has to offer in this 1900 square foot home positioned on a half-acre lot!  This home was built in 2007 with an open floor plan and split bedrooms. This home also features a new roof, volume ceilings, tons of natural light, water softener, factory tinted windows, newly screened lanai and tons of charm.  The large lot has plenty of room to build your own pool or grow your own garden.  The large kitchen features an island, black appliances and has plenty of room for the family to gather.  The primary bedroom is light and roomy with a walk-in closet and large bathroom with double sink vanity.  The property also features a large laundry room and programmable irrigation system for the lawn.  Location is minutes away from the business district of Lehigh Acres with shopping, banks, hospital, restaurants, schools, main highways to Fort Myers, and I-75.  Schedule a showing before this one is gone!
